ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Belarus) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (BELARUS) REGULATIONS in order to add twenty-one (21) individuals to Schedule 1 of the Regulations, prohibiting them from transacting business with individuals and businesses in Canada, and freezing their assets unless otherwise authorized by the Minister of the Foreign Affairs.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2024-0060 Publication Date: 2024-04-24
